1
00:01:27,060 --> 00:01:35,980
[Mga Pakikipagsapalaran ni Zhan Zhao]

2
00:01:35,980 --> 00:01:37,980
[Episode 1]

3
00:01:51,980 --> 00:01:56,620
[Shanbei Inn]

4
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,840
Waiter, isang tasa ng alak!

5
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:18,810
Paparating na!

6
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:23,390
Tagapangasiwa ng bahay-tuluyan,

7
00:02:23,930 --> 00:02:24,710
dalawang palayok doon.

8
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:25,810
Ipaupo mo sila.

9
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,060
Dahai, tumigil ka na sa pagkain.

10
00:02:48,180 --> 00:02:49,230
Kailangan na nating kumilos.

11
00:02:50,110 --> 00:02:50,740
Ikatlong Guro.

12
00:02:51,380 --> 00:02:52,130
Bumubuhos na ito.

13
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,060
Ano ba ang pagmamadali?

14
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,430
Gumagalaw tayo, may bagyo man o hindi.

15
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,120
May dala kaming mahalagang bagay,

16
00:02:56,380 --> 00:02:57,490
mas mabuting mag-ingat kaysa magsisi.

17
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:58,530
Isang huling subo na lang.

18
00:02:58,650 --> 00:02:59,490
Tara na pagkatapos ko.

19
00:04:16,250 --> 00:04:18,330
Ikaw ba si Ge Yunfei, ang Ikatlong Guro?

20
00:04:18,520 --> 00:04:19,260
ng Shengyun Mansion?

21
00:04:19,260 --> 00:04:21,580
[Ge Yunfei, Third Master ng Shengyun Manor]

22
00:04:21,980 --> 00:04:22,730
Iwanan ang bagay,

23
00:04:22,850 --> 00:04:23,930
at patatawarin ka namin.

24
00:04:24,150 --> 00:04:25,430
Alam mo kung sino ako,

25
00:04:26,250 --> 00:04:27,560
at nangangahas pa ring magnakaw sa akin?

26
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,090
Kung pwede mo lang itong nakawin,

27
00:04:30,180 --> 00:04:31,530
kaya rin natin.

28
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:36,530
Maglakas-loob ka bang tumawid sa Shengyun Manor?

29
00:04:36,530 --> 00:04:37,370
Patay ka na!

30
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:40,400
Kumusta!

31
00:04:45,450 --> 00:04:46,060
Angkan ng Tang.

32
00:04:48,100 --> 00:04:50,180
[Tang Jiujue, Wuning Hall ng Tang Clan]

33
00:04:54,550 --> 00:04:55,460
Nagtagpo ang ating mga landas!

34
00:06:14,230 --> 00:06:14,780
Mag-ingat!

35
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,330
Ayos ka lang ba?

36
00:07:06,380 --> 00:07:07,200
Nasaktan ka.

37
00:07:19,350 --> 00:07:20,360
Sino ang gumawa nito?

38
00:07:25,150 --> 00:07:26,290
Hindi ka ba makapagsalita?

39
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:28,640
Pero maririnig mo ako,

40
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,220
tama?

41
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:36,370
Kung malalaman ko

42
00:07:36,370 --> 00:07:37,500
sino ang nanakit sa iyo nang ganito,

43
00:07:38,390 --> 00:07:39,210
Hindi ko sila papakawalan.

44
00:07:54,730 --> 00:07:55,780
Mukhang may gusto ito sa iyo.

45
00:08:03,260 --> 00:08:03,940
Kakaiba.

46
00:08:04,030 --> 00:08:05,740
Yung amoy ng halamang gamot sa'yo...

47
00:08:05,930 --> 00:08:07,440
kadalasan ay ayaw nito sa amoy na iyon.

48
00:08:18,660 --> 00:08:20,210
Patay na ang lahat ng tao sa Shengyun Manor.

49
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:21,710
Kumusta ang pagbabalik mo?

50
00:08:23,660 --> 00:08:25,000
Hindi ka taga-Shengyun Manor?

51
00:08:27,530 --> 00:08:28,170
Kumusta naman ito?

52
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:30,340
Ang Xiangyang ang pinakamalapit mula rito.

53
00:08:30,530 --> 00:08:31,910
May ipapahatid ako sa iyo doon,

54
00:08:32,030 --> 00:08:33,140
saka natin ipapaalam sa mga awtoridad.

55
00:08:36,030 --> 00:08:36,810
Tagapangasiwa ng bahay-tuluyan.

56
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,580
Bumalik na naman sila!

57
00:08:49,950 --> 00:08:50,980
Bakit ka bumalik?

58
00:08:52,530 --> 00:08:53,980
Dapat nasa batang iyon ang gamit.

59
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:54,510
Hanapin siya.

60
00:08:55,950 --> 00:08:57,040
Bulag ka ba?

61
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,510
Halos hindi siya nakabihis.

62
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,540
Saan niya kaya maitatago ang kahit ano?

63
00:08:59,630 --> 00:09:00,710
Wala sa kanya 'yan,

64
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,040
kung gayon ay nasa iyo na iyon.

65
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,610
Magandang pamamaraan ng Cushion Palm.

66
00:09:13,790 --> 00:09:15,010
Saktan mo ako kung gusto mo,

67
00:09:15,130 --> 00:09:15,840
ngunit ang pambu-bully

68
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:16,900
isang batang walang kalaban-laban?

69
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:18,300
Sinisira talaga nito ang Tang Clan.

70
00:09:18,300 --> 00:09:19,340
Pangalan ng Wuning Hall.

71
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,350
Sino ka?

72
00:09:23,430 --> 00:09:24,010
Ikaw

73
00:09:24,530 --> 00:09:25,180
ngayon ay nasa pangalawa sa ranggo.

74
00:09:27,390 --> 00:09:28,930
Masyadong mababa ang ranggo ng dalawa pa,

75
00:09:29,230 --> 00:09:29,940
Hindi ko sila matandaan.

76
00:09:30,070 --> 00:09:31,770
Sino ang makakakita sa Listahan ng Dragon-Tiger,

77
00:09:32,330 --> 00:09:33,510
dapat alam mo nang mabuti 'yan.

78
00:09:33,830 --> 00:09:34,770
Dahil ikaw ay

79
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:35,770
isang kakampi, hindi isang kaaway,

80
00:09:35,930 --> 00:09:36,910
gawan mo kami ng pabor.

81
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:38,210
Huwag mo kaming pakialaman

82
00:09:38,330 --> 00:09:39,410
pagbawi ng ari-arian ng Tang Clan.

83
00:09:39,730 --> 00:09:40,740
Ari-arian ng Tang Clan?

84
00:09:41,330 --> 00:09:42,440
Kung ito ay kabilang sa Tang Clan,

85
00:09:42,730 --> 00:09:44,210
kung gayon bakit ito kasama sa Shengyun Manor?

86
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,620
Sigurado akong alam mo

87
00:09:45,730 --> 00:09:46,810
ang Tang Clan at Shengyun Manor

88
00:09:46,930 --> 00:09:47,710
matagal nang magkaaway.

89
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:48,700
Ano ang nangyari ngayon,

90
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:49,620
ang mga dahilan sa likod nito

91
00:09:49,660 --> 00:09:50,770
hindi para malaman ng mga tagalabas.

92
00:09:52,430 --> 00:09:53,670
Kung gayon, ano ang ginagawa

93
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:54,500
Ano ang hitsura ng item na ito ng Tang Clan?

94
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:55,400
May mga marka ba?

95
00:09:55,420 --> 00:09:56,140
Hayaan mong marinig ko.

96
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:59,240
Huwag mong sabihin sa akin na hindi mo rin alam iyon

97
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:00,610
at lumabas pa rin sa trabahong ito.

98
00:10:03,060 --> 00:10:03,440
Ayos lang.

99
00:10:03,470 --> 00:10:04,870
Kung patuloy kang makikialam dito,

100
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,110
ang buong Tang Clan

101
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,410
sisiguraduhin

102
00:10:07,530 --> 00:10:08,370
hindi mo na muling mararanasan ang kapayapaan.

103
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:14,390
Pagkatapos ay tanungin si Tang Tianhao

104
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:15,150
kung maglakas-loob siya.

105
00:10:15,390 --> 00:10:16,290
Hindi siya kailanman

106
00:10:16,290 --> 00:10:17,810
nagsalita sa akin nang ganyan.

107
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:19,520
Kung tatanungin mo ako,

108
00:10:19,730 --> 00:10:21,150
ang bagay na ito ay hindi kailanman naging

109
00:10:21,150 --> 00:10:22,310
mula sa Angkan ng Tang.

110
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:23,590
Kaya nga hindi mo masasabi

111
00:10:23,590 --> 00:10:24,140
kung ano ito.

112
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,010
O baka naman

113
00:10:25,530 --> 00:10:26,980
ito ay isang bagay na hindi mo kaya

114
00:10:27,860 --> 00:10:29,600
ipaalam sa iba ang tungkol dito.

115
00:10:30,460 --> 00:10:31,940
Gusto mo ba talagang malaman?

116
00:10:41,830 --> 00:10:42,770
Tanging...

117
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:44,580
kapag nalaman mo na,

118
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:46,370
wala nang buhay pagkatapos niyan!

119
00:10:50,790 --> 00:10:51,870
Dapat itong maging

120
00:10:51,870 --> 00:10:53,110
ang pinuno ng Shengyun Manor,

121
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,140
Jiao Chaogui

122
00:10:54,140 --> 00:10:55,260
[Jiao Chaogui, Shengyun Manor's Master]

123
00:10:55,260 --> 00:10:56,720
at Pangalawang Guro Mu Xiuquan.

124
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:57,670
[Mu Xiuquan]
Sino ang pumatay

125
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:58,340
[Shengyun Manor's Second Master]
Ge Yunfei?

126
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:01,310
Wala naman 'yun kinalaman sa amin.

127
00:11:01,390 --> 00:11:02,660
Ang pagkamatay ng iyong Ikatlong Guro

128
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,240
at kung saan napunta ang bagay na iyon...

129
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,610
silang tatlong iyon ang mas nakakaalam.

130
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:49,840
Ang malas naman ng araw na ito.

131
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:04,710
Seryoso?

132
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:06,020
Shengyun Manor

133
00:12:06,020 --> 00:12:07,560
ay labis na nagdusa mula sa Tang Clan.

134
00:12:08,230 --> 00:12:09,310
Bakit ba ang mga ito ay pabaya pa rin?

135
00:12:28,980 --> 00:12:29,560
Huwag mong intindihin nang mali.

136
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,640
Alam ko ang mga patakaran,

137
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,910
Wala akong kinakampihan kahit kanino.

138
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:33,810
Pasensya na po,

139
00:12:33,930 --> 00:12:34,510
pakituloy po.

140
00:12:45,630 --> 00:12:47,340
Humingi na ako ng tawad ngayon lang.

141
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:48,600
Bakit ayaw mo itong bitawan?

142
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:49,180
Gusto mo ba talaga akong patayin?

143
00:12:49,250 --> 00:12:50,110
Paano iyon posible?

144
00:12:50,280 --> 00:12:51,670
Hinaharangan ng Cushion Palm ang lahat ng armas.

145
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:54,570
May mali rito.

146
00:12:54,570 --> 00:12:55,110
Tara na muna tayo!

147
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:04,070
Taga-Linglong Manor ka ba?

148
00:13:05,550 --> 00:13:06,940
Dahil kaibigan ka ng pamilyang Huo,

149
00:13:07,030 --> 00:13:08,810
salamat sa pagtulong sa amin.

150
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:10,660
Kukunin namin ang bata ngayon.

151
00:13:10,780 --> 00:13:11,520
Hindi mo na kailangang magpasalamat sa akin.

152
00:13:11,650 --> 00:13:12,610
Ang ginawa ko ngayon lang

153
00:13:12,610 --> 00:13:13,590
hindi para tulungan ka.

154
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:15,120
Ang batang ito

155
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,400
ay hindi taga-Shengyun Manor.

156
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:17,780
Hindi mo siya maaaring ilayo.

157
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:21,110
Dahil pinipilit mong makialam,

158
00:13:21,560 --> 00:13:22,240
Ako

159
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,940
makakasakit lang sa damdamin ng pamilyang Huo!

160
00:14:10,610 --> 00:14:12,160
Ang iskor na ito sa pagitan mo at ng Tang Clan...

161
00:14:12,530 --> 00:14:13,170
Ako

162
00:14:13,270 --> 00:14:14,700
aayusin ko na lang sa iyo sa ibang araw!

163
00:14:35,060 --> 00:14:35,910
Saan ka pupunta?

164
00:14:41,730 --> 00:14:42,710
Xiangyang?

165
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,340
Dadalhin kita doon.

166
00:14:49,560 --> 00:14:50,640
Ayaw mo ba ng escort?

167
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:53,840
Pero ginawa ko talaga

168
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:55,410
ilalagay ang sarili ko sa malaking gulo.

169
00:14:55,790 --> 00:14:57,580
Natatakot ako kung pupunta ako sa Xiangyang kasama mo,

170
00:14:57,730 --> 00:14:58,540
Kakaladkarin kita diyan.

171
00:15:05,420 --> 00:15:06,160
Teka!

172
00:15:08,260 --> 00:15:09,410
Mas mabuting ihatid na lang kita doon,

173
00:15:09,560 --> 00:15:10,490
Masyado itong mapanganib.

174
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:12,310
Puro dugo ang mga damit mo,

175
00:15:12,860 --> 00:15:13,540
Masyado kang magiging kapansin-pansin diyan.

176
00:15:14,130 --> 00:15:14,810
Maghintay ka rito sandali,

177
00:15:15,060 --> 00:15:16,410
Ibibili kita ng malinis na damit.

178
00:15:17,930 --> 00:15:18,770
Hintayin mo ako,

179
00:15:19,740 --> 00:15:20,740
Babalik ako agad.

180
00:15:22,350 --> 00:15:23,240
Huwag kang umalis.

181
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,300
Ang mga pantalon na ito

182
00:15:31,300 --> 00:15:32,370
baka medyo matagalan ka,

183
00:15:32,460 --> 00:15:32,810
pero...

184
00:15:36,070 --> 00:15:36,610
Saan siya pumunta?

185
00:16:20,660 --> 00:16:22,300
[Feng Shao, Xiangzhou Military Envoy]

186
00:16:22,300 --> 00:16:23,850
Tumakbo ka agad pagkakita mo sa mga opisyal.

187
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,580
Siguradong may itinatago ka.

188
00:16:25,990 --> 00:16:26,850
Ibalik mo siya.

189
00:16:27,160 --> 00:16:28,210
Dahan-dahan natin siyang tatanungin.

190
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,140
Pusa!

191
00:16:36,230 --> 00:16:37,340
Pakuluan mo ako ng sabaw ng luya at mainit na tubig!

192
00:16:44,790 --> 00:16:45,110
Pumunta.

193
00:16:52,590 --> 00:16:53,190
Pusa!

194
00:16:53,380 --> 00:16:53,830
Lumabas ka rito!

195
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:54,860
Sugo Feng!

196
00:16:55,920 --> 00:16:56,500
Sugo Feng!

197
00:16:56,510 --> 00:16:58,030
Salamat naman at nandito ka!

198
00:16:58,040 --> 00:16:58,810
Kung hindi ka sana nagpakita agad,

199
00:16:58,810 --> 00:16:59,860
Pupunta rin sana ako sa mga awtoridad.

200
00:17:00,550 --> 00:17:01,290
Anong nangyari rito?

201
00:17:01,450 --> 00:17:02,330
Bakit ang daming patay dito?

202
00:17:03,250 --> 00:17:04,290
Huwag ka lang tumingin dito,

203
00:17:04,290 --> 00:17:06,260
may isa ring nakadikit sa loob.

204
00:17:12,580 --> 00:17:14,430
Sugo Feng, tingnan mo.

205
00:17:15,030 --> 00:17:15,590
Tingnan mo.

206
00:17:22,050 --> 00:17:22,830
Sino ang gumawa nito?

207
00:17:23,090 --> 00:17:23,830
Walang ideya.

208
00:17:25,980 --> 00:17:26,900
Kumusta naman yung apat sa labas?

209
00:17:27,050 --> 00:17:27,760
Hindi ko sila nakita kailanman.

210
00:17:28,650 --> 00:17:30,060
Nakikipaglokohan ka ba sa akin?

211
00:17:30,150 --> 00:17:30,900
Hindi ako maglalakas-loob.

212
00:17:30,980 --> 00:17:31,960
Yung nasa labas...

213
00:17:32,120 --> 00:17:33,060
Tatlong lalaking nakaitim ang pumatay sa kanya,

214
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:34,260
at agad silang tumakbo kasunod nito.

215
00:17:34,650 --> 00:17:35,960
Hindi ko alam kung sino sila.

216
00:17:36,180 --> 00:17:36,720
Tungkol naman sa isang ito,

217
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:37,400
Wala akong ideya

218
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,260
kung paano siya namatay.

219
00:17:38,450 --> 00:17:39,530
Mula sa sinasabi mo,

220
00:17:39,650 --> 00:17:40,620
malamang ang mamamatay-tao

221
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:41,940
hindi ito ang hinahanap natin.

222
00:17:42,180 --> 00:17:42,890
Magpadala ka ng mensahe.

223
00:17:52,710 --> 00:17:53,300
Sugo Feng,

224
00:17:53,380 --> 00:17:54,930
Sino ang sinenyasan mo kanina lang?

225
00:17:55,080 --> 00:17:56,730
Kung may darating na mas maraming panauhing may karangalan,

226
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:58,830
Makakapaghanda ang aking bahay-tuluyan para sa kanila.

227
00:17:59,450 --> 00:18:00,430
WHO?

228
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:03,560
Siyempre, ang aking superior.

229
00:18:03,780 --> 00:18:04,900
Ang aming Xiangzhou Prefecture

230
00:18:05,050 --> 00:18:06,300
Kumander ng Kabalyeriya,

231
00:18:06,550 --> 00:18:08,060
Panginoon Shao Jizu.

232
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:23,460
[Hangganan ng Yicheng County]

233
00:18:36,750 --> 00:18:37,250
Kumander Shao.

234
00:18:38,180 --> 00:18:39,350
[Shao Jizu, Xiangzhou Cavalry Commander]

235
00:18:39,350 --> 00:18:40,360
Nahanap na ba ang suspek?

236
00:18:41,580 --> 00:18:42,860
Hindi ako sigurado kung siya nga ba ang suspek,

237
00:18:43,180 --> 00:18:44,760
pero may kakaiba akong natuklasan.

238
00:18:55,980 --> 00:18:57,060
Malinaw na mayroon ang mga taong ito

239
00:18:57,070 --> 00:18:59,040
mga sugat sa talim, hindi mga sugat sa espada.

240
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:01,110
At namatay sila dahil sa lason.

241
00:19:01,450 --> 00:19:03,490
Malinaw na gawain iyon ng Tang Clan.

242
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:05,780
Hindi mo ba masasabi,

243
00:19:07,280 --> 00:19:09,160
o hindi mo man lang tiningnan?

244
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:10,830
Ang hindi ko maintindihan ay

245
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,490
kung bakit nandito ang Tang Clan.

246
00:19:13,080 --> 00:19:13,760
Maaari ba

247
00:19:13,950 --> 00:19:15,100
Hinahanap din ba nila ang taong iyon?

248
00:19:15,780 --> 00:19:17,600
May ibang plano ang amo para sa kanila.

249
00:19:20,080 --> 00:19:20,690
Sa loob,

250
00:19:21,120 --> 00:19:21,860
may isa pang bangkay.

251
00:19:38,710 --> 00:19:39,140
Hanapin ang lugar na ito

